results.title: X-Treme X-Men Vol. 3: Schism (Trade Paperback)
results.description:
They've accomplished their goal, but what will the X-Treme team do now? Join Storm, Wolverine. Bishop, Sage, and more of your favorite mutants for more romance, mystery and high-adventure.
Collects X-Treme X-Men #19-23 and X-POSE #1-2.

results.title: X-Treme X-Men Vol. 4 Mekanix (Trade Paperback)
results.description: Kitty Pryde's adventures in college! After experiencing the tragic loss of friends and family as a costumed hero, Kitty has made a decision to leave her former superhero life and forge a new one, on her own terms.  Unfortunately, the same bigotry and hatred that killed her loved ones continues to haunt her, threatening new and old friends alike. Collects the 6-issue MEKANIX limited series, plus X-MEN UNLIMITED #36

results.title: X-Treme X-Men Vol. 5: God Loves, Man Kills (Trade Paperback)
results.description:
Collecting the classic graphic novel by Chris Claremont and Brent Anderson (inspiration for the 2003 blockbuster X2), along with a brand new sequel to that legendary story! 
The Anti-Mutant Movement leader Stryker has returned and it's up to the X-Treme team to make sure his hatred of mutants does not lead to more deaths. But what happens when the X-Treme team and Stryker's goals are one and the same? Guest-starring Wolverine and Shadowcat!
Collects X-MEN: GOD LOVES, MAN KILLS GN, X-TREME X-MEN #25-30
